      "writtenOn": "2017-08-30T19:28:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is this intentionally one less than outer, as opposed to floor(radius)?  I guess it depends on what we want to do for integral radii -- should we fall back to the other impl in that case?\n\nAlso, do we sanitize sigma at some level to guarantee positive inner/outer radii?",
