      "writtenOn": "2017-08-30T20:08:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Since the inputs are specified as sigma for 0 \u003c sigma \u003c 2, there are two values that 1, 1 2/3. Looking at the top 10K web pages, those values never show. See included table.\n\nSanitized in ::blur, and FilterInfo.",
