      "message": "I don\u0027t quite follow how we arrive to 1.5 * sigma - 0.5.\n\nPer https://drafts.csswg.org/css-backgrounds-3/#shadow-blur, shouldn\u0027t that be 2 * sigma?\n\nWhat happens for sigma \u003c 1/3?  Looks like we cross into negative radius domain - do we need to clamp?",
